{"tid":2381272,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特斯拉與三星敲5奈米晶片協議 今年第四季量產、內建在自駕系統中","createTime":"2021-01-26T12:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T13:03:17.000Z","uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"25d33f27cd7c4e987efc93e61f8faf4ef67811f8","tid":2381272,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T12:28:19.000Z","msg":"南韓媒體傳出，特斯拉已跟三星電子敲定5奈米製程晶片協議，供應自動駕駛系統所需。<br />\n<br />\n根據外媒報導，業界消息顯示，三星晶圓代工部門正在進行5奈米系統半導體的研發計畫，這種半導體未來將內建於特斯拉自駕車。5奈米晶片必須應用極紫外光（EUV）微影設備，僅有三星、台積電等少數廠商有能力生產。<br />\n<br />\n報導稱，上述特斯拉最新晶片預計2021年第4季量產，意味著大眾要等到2022年才能看到內建這些晶片的特斯拉電動車。<br />\n<br />\n特斯拉的自動駕駛「Hardware 3.0」電腦晶片，即是由三星以14奈米製程打造。5奈米製程晶片直到2020年才開始應用於商業化產品，例如蘋果的iPhone 12。"},{"pid":"6faa060927ec18eda866245a36183cdcd0320b46","tid":2381272,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T12:28:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/61123/tesla-samsung-nanometer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bnext.com.tw%2Farticle%2F61123%2Ftesla-samsung-nanometer&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSvy3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=a3a33124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/61123/tesla-samsung-nanometer</a>"},{"pid":"df8bceaa407ef9540f2670af5fcb7462e0c406be","tid":2381272,"uid":17024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T12:28:49.000Z","msg":"曰日升<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86671624ed74ae7fca23c38b60b98afee2f2488","tid":2381272,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df8bceaa407ef9540f2670af5fcb7462e0c406be","tid":2381272,"uid":17024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T12:28:49.000Z","msg":"曰日升<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T12:29:25.000Z","msg":"不問價入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107a8d1901ca691b2431fc9f599ba60f499debf5","tid":